> T5E releases a new student survey <https://goo.gl/forms/FtDY7wvCRlROMcty1>:
> this one on gender based harassment in the institute.
>
> The objective of the survey is to draw a clearer picture of the state of
> affairs when it comes to gender related harassment in campus. However
> please note that this is not a comprehensive survey, *nor is it
> restricted to any particular gender*. Also note that the survey is
> strictly *anonymous.*
>
> Reliability of the data we collect depends partly on ensuring a large
> number of responses. Please take a few minutes to fill this survey and
> share it with your friends *irrespective of your experiences* and
> opinions on this issue. The survey responses will be made available on the
> website shortly.
